e general region where the ionizing flux is heavily broken,\nor the addition of collisional ionization to the simple photoionization models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 1998 03:52:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
